skdetail:

Invocation Name: math genius
des: You can choose to learn, practice or test your Math skills from 8 different levels, from easy to difficult. With regular practice, you will be able to perform calculations much faster than most people. Learn mode shows you examples and tips to calculate faster. Practice mode lets you apply what you learn to solve random exercises. Test mode makes it fun and grades you in a lightning round of ten questions. Let's get started now!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
